        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "Welcome to our first newsletter of 2017! It's been a while since the last one, and a lot has happened. We promise to keep them coming every two months hereafter, and permit ourselves to make this one rather long. The big news is the beginnings of our launch in the American market, but there are also interesting updates on sales, development, mentors and (of course) the investment round that closed in January.",
          "block_bbox": [
