        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "New capital: The investment round was successful. We raised 2.13 MNOK to match the 2.05 MNOK loan from Innovation Norway. Including the development agreement with Filmlance International, the total new capital is 5 MNOK, partly tied to the successful completion of milestones. All formalities associated with this process are now finalized.",
