          "block_content": "New owners: We would especially like to warmly welcome our new owners to the Drylab family: Unni Jacobsen, Torstein Jahr, Suzanne Bolstad, Eivind Bergene, Turid Brun, Vigdis Trondsen, Lea Blindheim, Kristine",
